2 CONT to Maria/Mariah. Father-in-law of Jacob Lake McClary. Buried Benton. His old farm later owned by Bruce Philpott. Receipt appears in Philip Cooper's 1845 estate settlement as 'Irby Boyd Receipt.' Death suggested in court Aug 1865 (p. 120).
1 NOTE (Merge artifact, flagged: the following note as merged described a SON of Erby Boyd Sr., not Erby Sr. himself.) Son of Erby Boyd Sr. and Jency Cooper. Buried Benton Cemetery. 2nd Lt., Co. B, 62nd Tenn. Mtd. Inf. (Confederate). Paroled Vicksburg
2 CONT July 1863. Married Harriet Elizabeth Biggs.

